pull_request.body:

comment.body:
I do not understand well your case.
So for example if the daemon version is default "development" string, we set the version to "0.0.0". In the update check will indicate that new version is available. I think this is the expected behavior.
I use equal instead of grater then because we would like to handle the downgrade events also.
